title: Wahoo's - West LA
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A "surf" tacos & Mexican fast food food chain, also called Wahoo's Fish Taco. The menu includes different filling choices for tacos, burritos, enchiladas, and bowls. Veg filling include marinated tofu, saute mixed vegetable teriyaki, or vegetarian rice and bean(with cheese). Vegans must specify; otherwise you might get cheese/dairy in your order.
